Cost-utility and cost-effectiveness of a guided self-help head and neck exercise 
program for patients treated with total laryngectomy: Results of a multi-center 
randomized controlled trial.

Jansen F(1), Coupé VMH(2), Eerenstein SEJ(3), Cnossen IC(3), van Uden-Kraan 
CF(4), de Bree R(5), Doornaert P(6), Halmos GB(7), Hardillo JAU(8), van Hinte 
